{"tid":127090,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【見工問呢啲】「你寧願睇父母上床定一齊3P？」 求職者嬲到呆","createTime":"2017-02-19T23:51:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-20T03:51:12.000Z","uid":1886,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"89c4c7ee85c7fcd7cd7f7b3420221a8f69bd7de4","tid":127090,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T23:51:47.000Z","msg":"【見工問呢啲】「你寧願睇父母上床定一齊3P？」 求職者嬲到呆<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20170219/56323965\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20170219%2F56323965&d=YBElpbzmALMQinc%2Bu7edPy7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=b032af68\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20170219%2F56323965&h=408c18dd\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20170219/56323965</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170219/large/1487476827_dfc6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170219%2Flarge%2F1487476827_dfc6.jpg&h=f444fc76&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n英國一位18歲求職者到連鎖餐廳面試時，竟然被考官問「你寧願看父母上床，或是一齊玩3P」，他深感被冒犯，最後未等面試完結即轉身離開，有關考官已被停職。<br />\n<br />\n來自德比郡的見習工程師多爾蒂（Daniel Dougherty）上周日參加TGI Fridays舉行的面試，有求職者被要求製作氣球，但多爾蒂卻在一場10分鐘面試中被問及奇怪問題。<br />\n<br />\n他憶述：「問答開始時很正常的，他問我之前的工作經驗，但5分鐘後面試官卻突然很奇怪。他問我會選擇看着父母上床一整年，還是一開始就加入玩3P，我很憤怒，我說這有悖倫理，我不打算回答。」<br />\n<br />\n之後對方還問他；「你寧願吃朱古力味的便便，還是便便味道的朱古力？」他深感有問題，他憶述當時的反應說：「我開玩笑說朱古力味的便便，之後便轉身離開。」<br />\n<br />\n餐廳知悉事件後已向多爾蒂道歉，強調有關問題不是面試過程一部份，並已將有關考官停職處分，又向多爾蒂提供第二次面試機會。不過多爾蒂發誓不再到TGI Fridays面試，「我可能以後都不會再去那兒吃飯」。"},{"pid":"777a99f11004c2c2c6f8e1e81ce386eb518efc05","tid":127090,"uid":41543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T23:53:43.000Z","msg":"應該答同考官老豆老母3P<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bfbd5631ee4b29416a11cb363b4fd97a1fa37ad","tid":127090,"uid":47966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T23:54:15.000Z","msg":"仲以係香港啲濕鳩人事部"},{"pid":"4d84414b1c0133c8c2d89ce22085ea02d9e55cd7","tid":127090,"uid":66260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T00:18:15.000Z","msg":"周x萍：有關問題純粹考面試者急才，考生應用智慧解答<br />\n當場離去為eq低表現"},{"pid":"3cb137e5197efb73f7ace1f457bf981cba97d64e","tid":127090,"uid":5499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T00:21:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>仲以係香港啲濕鳩人事部</blockquote><br />\n香港仲濕尻<br />\n<br />\n介唔介意加班"},{"pid":"6bc03e54c3993b8cd065c27be960a8f85d79be2c","tid":127090,"uid":42767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T01:04:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>周x萍：有關問題純粹考面試者急才，考生應用智慧解答<br />\n當場離去為eq低表現</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e5908fe4dced610ea22b1dc38bf1df4d8f57692","tid":127090,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T01:06:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好似睇過呢條問題"},{"pid":"f615cc68edec9818e3decb7aef321a1cd4697a5b","tid":127090,"uid":1637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T01:07:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>周x萍：有關問題純粹考面試者急才，考生應用智慧解答<br />\n當場離去為eq低表現</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你啱呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/34.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"901f60ac2d9ad28fe00d6d45f9a4fe2f0e9699e0","tid":127090,"uid":52056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T01:09:25.000Z","msg":"睇老豆老母扑嘢定一齊玩3P<br />\n食屎味朱古力定朱古力味屎<br />\n<br />\n餐廳有咩工需要做呢啲嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\